    /// tile `0..=1`). base `0x80A0_0000` (`[21]`=1 separates it from the FP32/FP16/BF16 outer products): Zm`[20:16]`,
    /// Pm`[15:13]`, Pn`[12:10]`, Zn`[9:5]`, `.h` marker`[3]`, tile`[1:0]` (`.s`) / `[0]` (`.h`).
