    /// load/store a horizontal/vertical `ZA` tile slice from/to memory (FEAT_SME). `store` picks `ST1`; `size` is the
    /// access/tile element; the slice is addressed by `za_tile`/`slice_offset`/`slice_reg` (`W12..W15`); the memory
